data.description: This beautiful 1.5 story home is located on a quiet cul de sac in a family-friendly neighborhood. A great option for qualified buyers is the assumable loan for 2.25% on the remaining loan balance of $309,000. The main level includes the open concept living room with wood floors, wood beams, fireplace and built in media console. The large kitchen includes a dining area, breakfast bar with extra storage, quartz countertops and stainless-steel appliances. The primary bedroom, with wood floors, tray ceiling and crown molding, and master bath are separate from the other two main level guest bedrooms and guest bath. The upper level includes a bedroom, full bath, classic plantation shutters, and walk-in attic for extra storage. Outside you'll find a screened porch overlooking the yard with wood privacy fence, dry riverbed with French drain, mature trees, plants and a gas grill. This beautiful home includes a storm shelter, security system and sprinkler system. Neighborhood amenities include walking trails, fishing pond, community garden, swimming pool, clubhouse, fitness center, playground and family recreational center.
